ExopyPulses Changelog
=====================


0.2.0 - unreleased
------------------

- drop Python 2 support
- use pytest-qt for the tests


0.1.0 - 15/02/2018
------------------

- rename project to exopy_pulses
- improve error message in sequence transfer task
- add a slope shape for pulses
- clean the context cache when cleaning all other caches
- add missing scroll area in the root sequence view


0.1.0.a3 - 24/11/2016
---------------------

- use ordered dinctionary for all variables (sequence_vars, external_vars, etc)
- support zeo duration pulses
- fix constraints of pulse view


0.1.0.a2 - 09/10/2016
---------------------

- Update sequence compilation logic : context has now full power on compilation
  and a standard pre-processing method is provided.
- fixes some issues in the UI


0.1.0.a1 - 29/09/2016
---------------------

- First numbered version
